text: Dragica Basletić (30 August 1916 - 26 August 1976) was a Croatian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Croatian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rijeka
